installation of the binary distribtution:
-----------------------------------------

- extract lisa-XXX-bin.tar.bz2 respective lisa-XXX-bin.zip to its final place

- start setup.tcl in the LiSA toplevel dir

- start LiSA with the "lisa" start script in LiSA/bin



installation of the source distribtution (UNIX like environments):
------------------------------------------------------------------

- make sure that tcl/tk and the g++ compiler are installed on your machine

- tar -xjvf lisa-XXX.tar.bz2

- cd LiSA

- ./configure

- edit Make.Config if configure is unable to find some of the includes or libraries

- make

- bin/lisa
